column5: Hi I know how you’re feeling. But they probably did have to go. You’re probably a really sweet and kind person! So try not to worry about stuff like that
Awww man I’m sorry. Maybe you can try to be friends first before you ask them out.
I would sleep all day if I could.

I hate that I always think negatively about everything. I’m just never going to be that positive person. Life is just pointless in general. When I’m having fun with my friends it’s just a moment in time. Life is just bad and sometimes good things happen.
Awww good morning! I hope you have a good day :3
That’s good that you’re living you’re life the way that you want. Mann I really just wish I could die. Oh well
I hate my face, the way my brain works. My life is so pointless all I do is work, eat, and sleep. Yeah sometimes I can be with friends and have fun. But the bad always out weighs the good.
Because I hate my life. I truly hate it and I hate myself sooooo fucking much. I just really want it to end.
I’m so fucking stupid. I just always do something so fucking dumb and this morning just sent me over the edge. It would just be a lot easier if I could just die.
